column5: Going in there now, just don't ask me any pointed, personal questions, keep it simple, lol.
Good to see you back Tom, I was wondering where you got to
Ummm..........Ok...........I mean, I needed a BREAK(not bread) from reality, lol

Haven't been really anywhere Lew, just up here doing what I had to do, and kicking myself in the hiny that I could not make it to Lakair this year.  And other stuff came up, and I was mad, and depressed, I just needed a break, plain and simple.
Good to see you back was wondering where you  were to. Hope all is right everyone needs a break from reality once in awhile.  Any fishing?
Welcome back Tom, was good to see ya back in chat last night!
Dang I missed you last night Bud welcome back.   Art
You weren't gone long enough for me to miss ya Bud, but welcome back anyhow.
Tom, it's good to have you off the DL and back to active duty.
Mad? depressed? what did you do with Wayne?(irishfield) I am not mad or depressed, crazy? maybe!
Nice to hear from you again Tom   Was wondering about you but figured you would post when you were ready...if you hadn't done it soon though I was thinking of sending out the dogs!   Welcome back!
Was good to have a chinwag with ya in chat last night.Dont be a stranger. Joe
Welcome back ya LWHL   Sorry I missed ya, it was passed my bedtime  Maureen
